      "platform": "meta",
      "type": "ad_status",
      "query": {
        "ds_id": "FA",
        "ds_accounts": "act_1417826285602744",
        "date_range_type": "yesterday",
        "fields": "Adcampaign_id,Adcampaign,Campaign_id,Campaign,Ad_id,Ad_name,Ad_status",
        "max_rows": 10000
      }
    }
  ],
  "notes": "Kenvue corporate-recruitment Meta ad account. Campaigns named 'Joveo | AB&C | Kenvue | Meta | <Country> | <Function>'. Verified 2026-05-26: ad-level query returns full Campaign\u2192AdSet\u2192Ad hierarchy. `Landing_page_views` is our v1 'applies' proxy (Joveo measures real applies ATS-side, not in Meta)."
